- [ ] Listing Detail page renders with media gallery, specs, AI QA, auction schedule, bid history, and CTAs; all data loaded with null-safety: items = data ?? [], Array.isArray checks, and useState([]) defaults for arrays.
- [ ] Bid flow: user can place immediate bids or configure proxy bids; server ensures concurrency-safe bidding; no race conditions; appropriate UI feedback on success/failure.
- [ ] Live Auction Room: real-time updates flow with Supabase Realtime/WebSocket; timer, bids, and chat updates propagate accurately to participants.
- [ ] Notifications: transactional emails/SMS dispatched with idempotent webhooks; in-app notifications respect user preferences.
- [ ] Caching: listing detail data served from edge/CDN with proper stale-while-revalidate strategy; backend queries optimized with indexing.
- [ ] AI QA: AI QA reports are pluggable; provider-agnostic adapters implemented; structured results rendered in UI with highlights and evidence.

